      "message_index": null,
      "entire_chat": "/chat/c0000005-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c005",
      "text": "Look up the Borg adaptive-shield signature 7-of-9-alpha and tell me if we have a counter on file.\n<details><summary>Tool use: starfleet_db_query — Querying Starfleet tactical DB</summary>\n\n```json\n{\n  \"signature\": \"7-of-9-alpha\",\n  \"table\": \"borg_shield_signatures\"\n}\n```\n</details>\n<details><summary>Tool use: starfleet_db_query — Retrying via backup relay</summary>\n\n```json\n{\n  \"relay\": \"backup-2\",\n  \"signature\": \"7-of-9-alpha\",\n  \"table\": \"borg_shield_signatures\"\n}\n```\n</details>\nYes — we have a counter on file. Rotating phaser modulation at 257.4 MHz (±0.6) gives roughly two effective rounds before the Borg re-adapt. Recommend pre-loading the rotation pattern before engagement.\n<details><summary>Tool result: starfleet_db_query (error)</summary>\n\n```\nERROR: connection to tactical-db.sf.test refused (subspace relay 4 offline)\n```\n</details>\n<details><summary>Tool result: starfleet_db_query</summary>\n\nSignature 7-of-9-alpha registered 2368-11-02. Counter: rotating phaser modulation 257.4 MHz ± 0.6. Effective rounds: 2 before re-adaptation.\n\n</details>",
